I wish that Quest was able to handle more than 2 numbers and an operation at a time.
So, you could go like: [code:1o5r1pj6]set numeric &lt;NNN;%AAA%+%ZZZ%+%DDF%+%YTYTY%&gt;[/code:1o5r1pj6]
Instead of having to go:[code:1o5r1pj6]set numeric &lt;NNN;%AAA%+%ZZZ&gt;
set numeric &lt;NNN;%NNN%+%DDF%&gt;
set numeric &lt;NNN;%NNN%+%YTYTY%&gt;[/code:1o5r1pj6]
